5. FinRobot: Generative Business Process AI Agents for Enterprise Resource Planning in Finance
Authors: Hongyang Yang et al.

Date: June 2025

Link: [arXiv:2506.01423](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2506.01423v1)

Why it matters: Introduces Generative Business Process AI Agents (GBPAs) for ERP systems in financial institutions. Validated on bank wire transfers and employee reimbursements, achieving 40% reduction in processing time, 94% drop in error rate, and improved regulatory compliance through automated risk control insertion.

For your team: If your compliance team is looking at agentic AI for KYC, AML, or transaction monitoring, this paper provides an architectural blueprint with empirical validation.

