🏛️ Central Bank & Regulatory Research Reports

8. Financial System Report Annex: Use and Risk Management of Generative AI by Japanese Financial Institutions
Publisher: Bank of Japan

Date: September 2025

Link: [BOJ Report](https://www.boj.or.jp/en/research/brp/fsr/fsrb250930.htm)

Key findings: Survey of 153 Japanese financial institutions. 50% already using GenAI; over 90% considering or trialing. Significant increase in institutions developing practical rules and organizational policies. However, 50% say there's "room for improvement" in monitoring usage, countermeasures against third-party risks, and cyberattack defenses.

For your team: A rare empirical look at how banks actually govern GenAI in practice — not just theory.

