12. Navigating the Future of Finance: The Transformative Role of Generative AI
Authors: Hassnian Ali, Ahmet Faruk Aysan

Journal: Journal of Central Banking Law and Institutions, Vol. 5(1), 2026

Link: [JCLI Article](https://doi.org/10.21098/jcli.v5i1.431)

Key findings: Uses Structured Topic Modelling (STM) on academic and grey literature. Academic discourse focuses on technical applications (portfolio optimization, forecasting); grey literature emphasizes ethical risks, regulatory challenges, and operational concerns. Identifies five future research areas: ethical governance, blockchain integration, employment impacts, AI-driven risk management, and personalized financial services.

For your team: A peer-reviewed academic lens on where the research frontier is — useful for aligning your team's R&D priorities with academic consensus.

